OL,3,C'I didn't know I was a young carer
OL,4,Cuntil my late teens ` it was my normal'
OL,6,FJenkin Edwards, who rose to fame on
OL,7,Fthe reality television show Big
OL,8,FBrother last year, has decided to use
OL,9,Fhis new platform to raise awareness of
OL,10,Fwhat life as a young carer is like.
OL,12,FBig Brother's Jenkin Edwards has
OL,13,Frevealed he didn't know he was a young
OL,14,Fcarer until his late teens, and now
OL,15,Fwants to reduce the stigma which many
OL,16,Fexperience.
