OL,3,C'I didn't know I was a young carer
OL,4,Cuntil my late teens ` it was my normal'
OL,6,FAround 11,000 children in Wales are
OL,7,Flooking after a member of their
OL,8,Ffamily, but with charities warning
OL,9,Fthat the pressure of being a carer can
OL,10,Fhave a terrible effect on a child's
OL,11,Fwell-being, there are calls for the
OL,12,FWelsh Government to do more to ease
OL,13,Fthe burden.
OL,15,FSpeaking to S4C's current affairs
OL,16,Fprogramme Y Byd ar Bedwar, the 26-year-
OL,17,Fold from Bridgend opened up about
OL,18,Fbeing a young carer for his mother.
