OL,3,C'I didn't know I was a young carer
OL,4,Cuntil my late teens ` it was my normal'
OL,6,FJenkin's mother has health issues
OL,7,Fwhich affect her mobility, and her son
OL,8,Fbecame a young carer at the age of 10.
OL,10,FHe said: "Her mobility was not great,
OL,11,Fit was a lot of personal care, helping
OL,12,Fher with everything she needed. For
OL,13,Fme, it was my normal.
OL,15,F"I never realised I was a young carer
OL,16,Funtil I was in my late teens. I
OL,17,Frealised then, 'actually not everyone
OL,18,Fis going through the things I do'.
