OL,3,C'I didn't know I was a young carer
OL,4,Cuntil my late teens ` it was my normal'
OL,6,F"I was shocked that there was no
OL,7,Ffunding left for certain things for
OL,8,Fyoung carers. I don't understand how
OL,9,Fit's fair that they are not getting
OL,10,Fthe funding that is going towards such
OL,11,Fa good thing and that they deserve."
OL,13,FAlthough Jenkin did not receive any
OL,14,Fsupport while growing up, his little
OL,15,Fsister attended the Young Carers
OL,16,FBridgend group which helped her
OL,17,Fthrough her caring role.
