OL,3,C'I didn't know I was a young carer
OL,4,Cuntil my late teens ` it was my normal'
OL,6,FMany young carers depend on the
OL,7,Fsupport given by Young Carers Bridgend
OL,8,Ffor respite, a space to talk, and to
OL,9,Fmeet other young people in the same
OL,10,Fposition.
OL,12,FBut the organisation is facing
OL,13,Ffinancial difficulties as they have
OL,14,Flost #30,000 from their budget this
OL,15,Fyear.
