OL,3,C'I didn't know I was a young carer
OL,4,Cuntil my late teens ` it was my normal'
OL,6,FAlissa Bevan, from Bridgend Carers
OL,7,FCentre, said: "We've received a lot
OL,8,Fmore referrals than we ever have
OL,9,Frecently, we're working really well
OL,10,Fwith all the schools, we've built
OL,11,Fgreat relationships with other
OL,12,Forganisations in the area, but we have
OL,13,Frecently lost some of our funding
OL,14,Fwhich means that there has been some
OL,15,Fcuts."
OL,17,FTo thank Young Carers Bridgend for
OL,18,Fsupporting his family, Jenkin has
OL,19,Fdecided to organise a fundraiser with
OL,20,Fthe hope to raise money for young
OL,21,Fpeople in need of support.
