OL,3,C'I didn't know I was a young carer
OL,4,Cuntil my late teens ` it was my normal'
OL,6,FJenkin said: "Seeing the difference it
OL,7,Fmade for my sister, the respite she
OL,8,Freceived, they even put her through
OL,9,Fher driving test. You know stuff like
OL,10,Fthat makes you realise how beneficial
OL,11,Fit is. And for me to be able to give
OL,12,Fback to an organisation that helped my
OL,13,Ffamily was just a no-brainer.
OL,15,FAnd he's even going to auction away
OL,16,Fhis famous green hoodie which he wore
OL,17,Foften in the Big Brother house.
