OL,6,F"In addition to this we have provided
OL,7,F#700,000 to establish a young carer ID
OL,8,Fcard scheme for use in schools across
OL,9,FWales, and provide additional
OL,10,Feducational resources and networks to
OL,11,Fsupport young carers. We have also
OL,12,Fsupported three annual festivals for
OL,13,Fyoung carers with #140,000. These
OL,14,Fprovide extra-curricular activities
OL,15,Fand experiences for young carers which
OL,16,Fwe know has a positive impact on
OL,17,Faspirations and attainment.
